HEADWORD: Propination
<hw>Prop`i*na"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>propinatio</ets>. See <er>Propine</er>.]</ety> <def>The act of
pledging, or drinking first, and then offering the cup to another.</def>
